                "invention-title": [
                    "Synthesis method of chromium ion doped tungsten oxide complete photolysis water catalyst flat reactor",
                    "一种铬离子掺杂氧化钨完全光解水催化剂平板反应器的合成方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a synthesis method of a chromium ion doped tungsten oxide complete photolysis water catalyst flat plate reactor, which comprises the following steps: 1, fully dissolving sodium tungstate and chromium acetate in water, and mixing with glacial acetic acid to obtain a reaction solution, with the volume ratio of water to glacial acetic acid being 1: 1, the concentrations of the sodium tungstate, the chromium acetate, the citric acid or the trisodium citrate are 0.01-1 mol L1, 1 * 10 &lt; 3 &gt;-0.4 mol L1 and 0-2 mol L1 respectively, and the molar ratio of the sodium tungstate to the chromium acetate to the citric acid or the trisodium citrate in the solution is kept to be 1: (0.1-0.4): (0-2), and then the solution is transferred to a stainless steel autoclave reactor with a polytetrafluoroethylene lining. According to the synthesis method, the activity (solar energy-hydrogen (STH) conversion efficiency value is 4.3%-6.1%) of the complete photolysis water catalyst is remarkably improved, the service life of the complete photolysis water catalyst is remarkably prolonged, and the cost price of the complete photolysis water catalyst is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种铬离子掺杂氧化钨完全光解水催化剂平板反应器的合成方法，包括以下步骤：步骤一：将钨酸钠和乙酸铬充分溶于水后再与冰乙酸混合获得反应溶液，水与冰乙酸的体积比为1:1，其中，钨酸钠、乙酸铬、柠檬酸或柠檬酸三钠浓度分别为0.01~1 mol L−1、1×10−3~0.4 mol L−1、0~2 mol L−1，并且保持溶液中的钨酸钠、乙酸铬、柠檬酸或柠檬酸三钠摩尔比为1:0.1~0.4:0~2，随后转移至具有聚四氟乙烯内衬的不锈钢高压釜反应器中。本发明的合成方法显著提高完全光解水催化剂活性（太阳能→氢（STH）转化效率值4.3%~6.1%）、使用寿命，并降低其成本价格。"
                }
            ]
